==English==

===Etymology===
From [[donation]] + [[ware]] a contraction of [[software]]

===Noun===
'''donationware'''

#{{cattag|Internet}} A variant of [[freeware]] that offers an option to its user to donate money to the program's author. In cases where the request to donate money nags the user with each application of the program's use, this is called [[nagware]].

